Titolo: Boyfriend Dungeon

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Boyfriend Dungeon is a dungeon crawler-dating sim indie game developed and published by Kitfox Games. Taking place in an urban fantasy setting, the player character must fight through dungeons with the help of a human partner who can transform into a sentient weapon. Outside of dungeons, the player can date their partner in visual novel-style sequences that increase their power in combat. It was released for the Nintendo Switch, Xbox One and PC on August 11, 2021.

Genere: Dungeon crawler

Valutazione: 71
